        ## Installation
        ### as a standalone lib.
        ```bash
        # Set up a virtualenv. 
        python3 -m venv venv
        source venv/bin/activate
        
        # Install from PyPI...
        pip install --upgrade pip
        pip install -U repoly
        
        # ...or, install from updated source code.
        pip install git+https://github.com/davips/arqgen-challenge/repoly
        ```
        
        
